column5: 12 pounds 6 ounces... What a beauty!!!    Going after salmon with Dan Bouck and my old man in the morning then hitting up the facts of fishing kids day!  Have a good Saturday guys!  Cheers, Ryan
AHH HAHAHAHAHA  Good one Ryan!  Too bad it's my daughters b-day weekend or we would be there tomorrow too...
Use the Bocagrip on that thing, are you crazy!?!?!??!?!!!
wow nobody can beat that!... lolz
I didn't know we could count babies!
Nice clean specimen and look at the colours on her! Great shot, Ryan.  ps. WAKE UP!
Won't be long and she will have control of that bait caster. She definitely is a keeper.
